  "page": "Battle of Three Armies",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle of Three Armies</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">Gardener</a> victory</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\"><img alt=\"House Gardener.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/20px-House_Gardener.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/30px-House_Gardener.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/40px-House_Gardener.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Reach\" title=\"King of the Reach\">Kingdom of the Reach</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/20px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/40px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rock\" title=\"King of the Rock\">Kingdom of the Rock</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Kingdom of the Storm</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\"><img alt=\"House Gardener.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/20px-House_Gardener.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/30px-House_Gardener.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f2/House_Gardener.svg/40px-House_Gardener.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Garth_VII_Gardener\" title=\"Garth VII Gardener\">Garth VII Gardener</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/20px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/40px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rock\" title=\"King of the Rock\">King of the Rock</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/20px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/30px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/40px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Strength</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">unknown</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      unknown</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Battle of Three Armies</b> was a battle between <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/The_Reach\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Reach\">the Reach</a> and an alliance of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rock\" title=\"King of the Rock\">Rock</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_Three_Armies&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In his last and greatest war, King <a href=\"/index.php/Garth_VII_Gardener\" title=\"Garth VII Gardener\">Garth VII Gardener</a> of the Reach faced an alliance between the <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rock\" title=\"King of the Rock\">King of the Rock</a>, who intended to divide the Reach between them. Garth defeated them both, and then with cunning words he sowed such discord between the two kings that they turned on each other with great slaughter. In the aftermath Garth married his daughters to their heirs and signed a pact with each, thereby fixing the borders between their three kingdoms.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_Three_Armies&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_gardener_kings.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Gardener Kings.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404204449\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.073 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.253 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 329/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9294/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8